&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of Linux Kernel and drivers is a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of storage architectures and system-level debugging is also beneficial. Experience with bus analyzers and trace evaluation tools is required.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Programming Proficiency:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong proficiency in programming languages such as python, C and C

